{"tid":412434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT男富亨邨墮樓分屍!!!!","createTime":"2017-09-24T16:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T09:17:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff92ee23d02028a91ccebdbc2aad0b0fed543488","tid":412434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"大埔富亨邨男子墮樓亡，下午1時27分，一名34歲姓梁男子被發現由高處墮下，倒臥在亨盛樓對開分屍慘死，保安員聞訊報警。警方到場調查，分別取來帳篷及白布將屍身遮蓋，相信梁墮下時砸毀一樓一個晾衫架，地上遺下拖鞋、衫及背囊。警方聯絡上死者一男2女親友到場認屍，眾人傷心不已，其中一名婦人情緒激動，哭至死去活來，需要警方借來圓櫈給其休息。<br />\n<br />\n警方未檢獲遺書，初步認為無可疑，正調查其墮樓原因。據悉，梁任職<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊科技工作</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170924/bkn-20170924143920479-0924_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170924%2Fbkn-20170924143920479-0924_00822_001.html&d=pLan3%2BEzrGXuMZG5Q%2Ft0sdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f624a513\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170924/bkn-20170924143920479-0924_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"83b3db89d8735a2e4a6a77a58cfda31843278a63","tid":412434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">任職資訊科技工作<br />\n任職資訊科技工作<br />\n任職資訊科技工作</span>"},{"pid":"2e2de61dbfb4a2692bdd714bcc4da77ee9a3e355","tid":412434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"none care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5031f872e11765c450a5d42c5d78fca7a171ed3","tid":412434,"uid":72736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94a646b35ce08845caf832c432eb55748336739","tid":412434,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"老世：正！唔洗出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"